{"tid":244220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【長毛發功】「翠如BB股」被點相 David Webb指聯旺不能買！","createTime":"2017-05-15T09:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T09:16:40.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"967f7e4d965fe022c446fcae6a83bcf52a5d5f88","tid":244220,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/171257_537d4e4a2f01e44911e92e10be0ce30f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F171257_537d4e4a2f01e44911e92e10be0ce30f.jpg&h=3916191c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「股壇長毛」David Webb今日在其網站發佈「50隻不能買的港股」名單，上榜多數為細價股，其中以「翠如BB股」 聯旺集團（8217）市值最高，達236億元。由於聯旺股權高度集中，成交極為疏落，今日再度無成交，報18.96元。<br />\n<br />\n由藝人黃翠如父親黃永華任大股東的聯旺集團（8217），股價由2016年4月上市至今，由招股價0.26元 扶搖直上，股價至今爆升73倍。聯旺上市當日，因大股東黃永華女兒「翠如BB」現身港交所， 吸引傳媒蜂擁而上採訪，令股票聲名大噪。而聯旺越升越有， 傳媒就經常同翠如BB「數身家」，「千金指數」比恆指更吸引。<br />\n<br />\n證監會在去年4月指，聯旺股權高度集中，連同大股東在內廿名人士股權，共持有聯旺超過95%股份，散戶街貨量不足5%，意味股價有機會大幅波動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56696662&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56696662%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=945664ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56696662%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&h=1bf2b8ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56696662&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515</a>"},{"pid":"388b0057c9be9f8ad6c7239abc3705cfa0dd2aa5","tid":244220,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"創仔唔講<br />\n主板果堆有玩開細股一早知係咩股黎啦<br />\n但錢永遠都係靠呢d贏"}]}